            <div type="transcript" id="J274">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>The only Ghost I ever saw</l>
                    <l>Was dressed in Mechlin -- so --</l>
                    <l>He <app type="revision"><lem>wore --</lem><rdg>wore --</rdg></app>
had no sandal on his foot --</l>
                    <l>And stepped like flakes of snow --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>His Mien, was soundless, like <app type="revision"><lem>a --</lem><rdg>a --</rdg></app>
the Bird --</l>
                    <l>But rapid -- like the Roe --</l>
                    <l>His fashions, quaint, Mosaic --</l>
                    <l>Or haply, Mistletoe --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>His conversation -- seldom --</l>
                    <l>His laughter, like the Breeze</l>
                    <l>That dies away in Dimples</l>
                    <l>Among the <app type="revision"><lem>smiling</lem><rdg>smiling</rdg></app>
pensive Trees --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Our interview -- was transient --</l>
                    <l>Of me, himself was shy --</l>
                    <l>And God forbid I look behind --</l>
                    <l>Since that appalling Day!</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>5.Mien] Gait --</l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
